		{"id":"2d0da488eb5cb3f7","type":"text","text":"#### Enable CORS\n\n###### [django-cors-header 官方文件](https://github.com/adamchainz/django-cors-headers)\n\n###### Step1: 安裝套件\n\n```bash\npip install django-cors-headers\n```\n\n###### Step2: 將 App 加入 settings.py\n\n```Python\nINSTALLED_APPS = [\n    ...,\n    \"corsheaders\",\n    ...,\n]\n```\n\n###### Step3: 加入 Middleware\n\n盡量放在越前面越好：\n\n```Python\nMIDDLEWARE=[\n    ...,\n    \"corsheaders.middleware.CorsMiddleware\",\n    \"django.middleware.common.CommonMiddleware\",\n    ...,\n]\n```\n","x":-305,"y":-164,"width":529,"height":848},
		{"id":"25349c4467cc6335","type":"text","text":"#### 自訂 HTTP Headers\n\n若前後端溝通時想要有標準 HTTP headers 以外的自訂 headers，則 Django 後端必須額外做設定，後端才不會因為看見陌生的 header 而將前端的 `GET` 或 `POST` method 歸類為 `OPTION` method。\n\n以下假設你的 Django Framework 有安裝 `django-cors-headers` 這個套件。\n\n比如現在前後端想制定一個名為 \"identity\" 的 header，後端設定的方法很簡單，只要在 `settings.py` 中做以下設定即可：\n\n```Python\n# settings.py\n\nCORS_ALLOW_HEADERS = list(default_headers) + [\"identity\"]\n```\n\n須注意的是，在 Django 若要讀取 identity header 的值，則實際上要讀取的是 HTTP_IDENTITY:\n\n```Python\nrequest.META.get(\"HTTP_IDENTITY\")\n```\n","x":322,"y":-164,"width":686,"height":658},
		{"id":"7f165748c7e35d45","type":"text","text":"#### Admin 忘記密碼的解決辦法\n\n忘記密碼的解決辦法就是重設密碼，沒有辦法直接將原密碼取回，因為 DB 裡存的都是經過 hash 的密碼，無法將其還原為 plaintext。重設密碼的步驟如下：\n\n- Step1: Navigate to the project root directory, i.e. where your \"manage.py\" file is located.\n- Step2: Enter the Python interpreter (with Django settings loaded)\n\n    ```bash\n    python manage.py shell\n    ```\n\n- Step3\n\n    ```Python\n    from django.contrib.auth.models import User\n\n    # Get all users\n    users = User.objects.all()\n\n    # Select the user you wish to change their password (The first user is usually the admin)\n    user = users[0]  # just for example\n\n    # Set the password and save the user\n    user.set_password(\"your new password\")\n    user.save()\n    ```\n\nDone!\n\n###### 參考資料\n\n- <https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6358030/how-to-reset-django-admin-password>","x":1154,"y":-164,"width":822,"height":864},
